AGI - After almost nine hours the questioning river of the president of the Liguria Region Giovanni Toti>, which is still in the barracks of the Roan of the Gdf for the signature of the minutes. The governor, according to his trap, responded to all the complaints made by the Prosecutor, assisted by his lawyer Stefano Savi. Toti also deposited a 17-page memory of the investigative interrogation held in front of Federico Manotti and Luca Monteverde, along with the adjunct Vittorio Ranieri Miniati. A document to explain "the political and moral lines that, from what I assumed the honor of leading Liguria Region, have always informed the activity pursued by the Regional Council in the only perspective of serving the good and common interest of Ligurian citizens and their institutions".
&nbsp;
"It is not my intention to withdraw from your examination, but today, as in the future, there is my firm will to collaborate, with transparency and honesty, to the reconstruction of Truth in the supreme interest of Justice, to return to my figure of man and to serve the State the Dignity I have constantly tried to preserve," writes the governor in memory. "In my political path - he writes - I have always pursued the public interest which is the sole and final end of my political action; This goal is followed, as constantly claimed by the political programme of the majority that supports me, not already through the opposition with the demands of the private, but rather through the conveyance of these towards the interest of the community and the territory, how the best essence of public interest is achieved." &nbsp;
&nbsp;
"It is from a wide-ranging vision, that embraces all the course of my presidency, that we can appreciate our political vision and fully understand how all my actions (even those contested) have been inspired, certainly by the right attention to the companies operating on the territory, but in the only perspective of the protection of the collective interest and its progress," continued Toti, "the policy of openness to the world of the enterprise, the need to make more celerious and &nbsp;
<h2>"No personal enrichment or utility"</h2>
"Every Euro cashed has had a political destination: no contribution has produced personal enrichment or usefulness to me, to others belonging to my party or to private third parties", writes Toti, "and precisely to escape every possible suspicion and guarantee maximum transparency and possibility of control, particular attention - continues - has been placed in separating every economic aspect of my private life from any economic activity linked to politics, so as to separate also personal current accounts and use for the political activity exclusively dedicated and "transparent"
&nbsp;
The governor speaks of "transparent management of public affairs and politics. As well as any intervention in favor of the economic initiatives has been public, often through specific communications (see the countless outsourcing on the harbour balances to be reached for public interest), even every dation of money is rash in the maximum transparency. This - it emphasizes - is recognized by the same acts of accusation where reference is made to real transfers to the Political Committees, managed in the legal principles of maximum transparency, with objectives and statutory bodies and balance sheets published according to law. Each share of money has been credited with traceable methods and reporting. Equally all expenses incurred (both in support of my political activity as leader of the Toti List present in the Regional Council and in many municipal administrations, and in support of mayors, lists and candidates linked and consistent with the Toti List political line, both with regard to the initiatives of the Government Coalition) have been reported and advertised in terms of law and also beyond. Budgets and reports have been (and are still) published on the websites of political organizations in my support". &nbsp;
&nbsp;
"I never felt compelled to those who contributed to my political initiative: the fact of being a contributor or, however, politically close has never been a title to receive favours or preferential treatments from me; There has never been any attitude of mine that could somehow give rise to such thought. There was - it emphasizes - simply a broad and widespread vision from the private about the utility, civic and economic, to support an administration that saw in private investment, within the rules, a means to pursue a public interest, as well as private. The vision corresponded to the maximum administrative commitment to support and if possible to facilitate investment and business activities regardless of the political colour of the enterprises themselves".
<h2>"I met the Head Brothers twice"</h2>
"With regard to the vote of exchange, it should be noted that I won the elections with about 380 thousand votes. The support of the Riesina community rests, in the investigations, with a certain approximation, of 400 votes, just by proportion and to understand that the contribution is not such as to disturb the democratic balance of the vote, however particularly irrelevant in the case of the candidate, Ilaria Cavo, to which my support is attributed", writes the governor, adding that "the Head brothers were presented as political activists with assignments in the Lombardy Region by two Honours. In their curriculum there were political assignments related to the Lombard Regional Council. Both Honourables (Sorte and Benigni) guaranteed their personal qualities. The same, on social (and formally) were official representatives of the Riesine Community in the World: the fact of being riesini and their representatives cannot be equal to being considered as people of mistrust. Analogue attention to groups organized representatives of citizens of common extraction (Lucani, Calabrians in the world) is provided by the policy of each color in order to collect their consent".
&nbsp;
Toti writes that he met "the Head brothers at most twice. Their interest was aimed at the possible attention to a community, that Riesina, often subject to all difficulties related to immigration and integration in different regions. I certainly sent my employees to give them attention in terms of law. But never offer usefulness in exchange for votes. The general promise of a better personal and social condition cannot be considered as a commodity of exchange but customary fruit of political activity, especially during the electoral period; expected that I did not know, if not now, of the promises made to some (limited) members of the community, the signaling to private enterprises of some of them as masons or maneuvers (other than never assumed), such activity if it had been known to me, and was not, without being aware of any previous agreements, would have been interpreted as support to people in difficulty. And also the request for a shift of residence from one popular house to another (for other already assigned) appears as merely informative support to a person with the obvious little skills in deduction in public administration. Moving for other things never happened".
&nbsp;
Toti concludes that "at the end of a long reconstruction, no specific utilities went to the Riesina community, neither in jobs nor other. As it is evident from the same investigations of insistent people for behavior and expressions, it is possible that some jokes between me and the staff were interpreted outside the context with which the theme of riesini was addressed in meetings." &nbsp;
